<exercise id="fs-idp298677568">
<problem id="fs-idp16592128">
<para id="fs-idm58721440">Notaðu lotukerfið til að spá fyrir
um hvort eftirfarandi klóríð séu jóna- eða samgild: KCl, NCl<sub>3</sub>, ICl,
MgCl<sub>2</sub>, PCl<sub>5</sub> og CCl<sub>4</sub>.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp129483232"><para id="fs-idm4134080">Jónaefni: KCl, MgCl<sub>2</sub>; Samgild:
NCl<sub>3</sub>, ICl, PCl<sub>5</sub>, CCl<sub>4</sub></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp44267360">
<problem id="fs-idp65122256">
