<exercise id="fs-idp221295264">
<problem id="fs-idp278674944">
<para id="fs-idp95603488">Fyrir hvert eftirfarandi
efnasambanda, tilgreindu hvort það sé jóna- eða samgilt. Ef það er
jónaefni, skrifaðu táknin fyrir jónirnar sem um ræðir:</para>
<para id="fs-idp63096544">(a) NF<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp175705168">(b) BaO</para><para id="fs-idp210482672">(c) (NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm16898128">(d) Sr(H<sub>2</sub>PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp523680">(e) IBr</para>
<para id="fs-idp18583904">(f) Na<sub>2</sub>O</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm3993968"><para id="fs-idp108175056">(a) samgilt; (b) jónaefni,
Ba<sup>2+</sup>, O<sup>2−</sup>; (c) jónaefni, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:msup><m:mtext>,</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2−</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (d)
jónaefni, Sr<sup>2+</sup>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>−</m:mo></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (e) samgilt; (f) jónaefni, Na<sup>+</sup>,
O<sup>2−</sup></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp4856416">
<problem id="fs-idp164870384">
<para id="fs-idp133547504">Fyrir hvert eftirfarandi
efnasambanda, tilgreindu hvort það sé jónaefni eða samgilt, og ef það er
