<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idp97231552">
<term>samgilt tengi (e. covalent bond)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp97231552-meaning">aðdráttarkraftur milli
kjarna atóma sameindar og rafeindapara milli atómanna</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp184530720">
<term>samgilt efnasamband (e. covalent compound)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp184530720-meaning">(einnig
sameindaefnasamband) samsett úr sameindum sem myndaðar eru af atómum
tveggja eða fleiri mismunandi frumefna</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp160949776">
<term>jónatengi (e. ionic bond)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp160949776-meaning">rafstöðukraftar
aðdráttar milli gagnstætt hlaðinna jóna jónaefnis</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp182712496">
<term>jónaefni (e. ionic compound)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp182712496-meaning">efnasamband sem
samanstendur af katjónum og anjónum í ákveðnum hlutföllum sem gefa
rafhlutlaust efni</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp93864192">
<term>sameindaefnasamband (e. molecular compound)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp93864192-meaning">(einnig, samgilt
efnasamband) samsett úr sameindum sem myndast af atómum tveggja eða
fleiri mismunandi frumefna</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp136404896">
<term>einatóma jón (e. monatomic ion)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp136404896-meaning">jón sem samanstendur af
einu atómi</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp484916992">
<term>oxóanjón (e. oxyanion)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp484916992-meaning">fjölatóma anjón sem
samanstendur af miðatómi sem er tengt súrefnisatómum</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp93746160">
<term>fjölatóma jón (e. polyatomic ion)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp93746160-meaning">jón sem samanstendur af
fleiri en einu atómi</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
